variantsSampleFieldsList.name: ALT
variantsSampleFieldsList.description: Comma separated list of alternate non-reference alleles called on at least one of the samples
variantsSampleFieldsList.label: ALT

variantsSampleFieldsList.name: ID
variantsSampleFieldsList.description: Semi-colon separated list of unique identifiers where available
variantsSampleFieldsList.label: ID

variantsSampleFieldsList.name: INFO_AF
variantsSampleFieldsList.description: Allele frequency based on Flow Evaluator observation counts
variantsSampleFieldsList.label: INFO_AF

variantsSampleFieldsList.name: INFO_DP
variantsSampleFieldsList.description: Total read depth at the locus
variantsSampleFieldsList.label: INFO_DP

variantsSampleFieldsList.name: INFO_FDP
variantsSampleFieldsList.description: Flow Evaluator read depth at the locus
variantsSampleFieldsList.label: INFO_FDP

variantsSampleFieldsList.name: INFO_FR
variantsSampleFieldsList.description: Reason why the variant was filtered.
variantsSampleFieldsList.label: INFO_FR

variantsSampleFieldsList.name: INFO_FSAF
variantsSampleFieldsList.description: Flow Evaluator Alternate allele observations on the forward strand
variantsSampleFieldsList.label: INFO_FSAF

variantsSampleFieldsList.name: INFO_FSAR
variantsSampleFieldsList.description: Flow Evaluator Alternate allele observations on the reverse strand
variantsSampleFieldsList.label: INFO_FSAR

variantsSampleFieldsList.name: INFO_FSRF
variantsSampleFieldsList.description: Flow Evaluator Reference observations on the forward strand
variantsSampleFieldsList.label: INFO_FSRF

variantsSampleFieldsList.name: INFO_FSRR
variantsSampleFieldsList.description: Flow Evaluator Reference observations on the reverse strand
variantsSampleFieldsList.label: INFO_FSRR

variantsSampleFieldsList.name: INFO_HRUN
variantsSampleFieldsList.description: Run length: the number of consecutive repeats of the alternate allele in the reference genome
variantsSampleFieldsList.label: INFO_HRUN

variantsSampleFieldsList.name: INFO_HS
variantsSampleFieldsList.description: Indicate it is at a hot spot
variantsSampleFieldsList.label: INFO_HS

variantsSampleFieldsList.name: INFO_OMAPALT
variantsSampleFieldsList.description: Maps OID,OPOS,OREF,OALT entries to specific ALT alleles
variantsSampleFieldsList.label: INFO_OMAPALT

variantsSampleFieldsList.name: INFO_PB
variantsSampleFieldsList.description: Bias of relative variant position in reference reads versus variant reads. Equals Mann-Whitney U rho statistic P(Y>X)+0.5P(Y=X)
variantsSampleFieldsList.label: INFO_PB

variantsSampleFieldsList.name: INFO_PBP
variantsSampleFieldsList.description: Pval of relative variant position in reference reads versus variant reads.  Related to GATK ReadPosRankSumTest
variantsSampleFieldsList.label: INFO_PBP

variantsSampleFieldsList.name: INFO_RBI
variantsSampleFieldsList.description: Distance of bias parameters from zero.
variantsSampleFieldsList.label: INFO_RBI

variantsSampleFieldsList.name: INFO_SAF
variantsSampleFieldsList.description: Alternate allele observations on the forward strand
variantsSampleFieldsList.label: INFO_SAF

variantsSampleFieldsList.name: INFO_SAR
variantsSampleFieldsList.description: Alternate allele observations on the reverse strand
variantsSampleFieldsList.label: INFO_SAR

variantsSampleFieldsList.name: INFO_SRF
variantsSampleFieldsList.description: Number of reference observations on the forward strand
variantsSampleFieldsList.label: INFO_SRF

variantsSampleFieldsList.name: INFO_SRR
variantsSampleFieldsList.description: Number of reference observations on the reverse strand
variantsSampleFieldsList.label: INFO_SRR

variantsSampleFieldsList.name: INFO_STB
variantsSampleFieldsList.description: Strand bias in variant relative to reference.
variantsSampleFieldsList.label: INFO_STB

variantsSampleFieldsList.name: INFO_STBP
variantsSampleFieldsList.description: Pval of Strand bias in variant relative to reference.
variantsSampleFieldsList.label: INFO_STBP

variantsSampleFieldsList.name: INFO_TYPE
variantsSampleFieldsList.description: The type of allele, either snp, mnp, ins, del, or complex.
variantsSampleFieldsList.label: INFO_TYPE

variantsSampleFieldsList.name: REF
variantsSampleFieldsList.description: The value in the POS field refers to the position of the first base in the String
variantsSampleFieldsList.label: REF
